Mobility equipment

  • Rollator (walker w/seat)

    • Steel frame construction safely supports users up to 300 lbs
    • Partially covered by Medicare and Medicaid
    • Designed with folding hinge for easy storage and portability
    • Lever allows for independent handle height and angle adjustment
    • Oversized padded seat and backrest are made of strong polyurethane material for durability
    • 7 1/2-inch, non-marring casters are ideal for indoor and outdoor use
    • Includes fabric storage pouch for conveniently transporting personal items
    • Assorted colors
    • Manufacturer: McKesson

  • Nitro Rollator

    • Attractive, euro-style design
    • Handle height easily adjusts with unique push button
    • Designed with folding hinge for easy storage and portability.
    • Back support height easily adjusts with tool-free thumb screw
    • Large 10 inch front casters allow optimal steering and rolling comfort
    • Cross-brace design allows for side-to-side folding and added stability
    • Manufacturer: Drive

  • Aluminum Folding Walker

    • Adult folding paddle walkers with 5” wheels
    • Approximate user height: 5’5” - 6’4” (165 - 193 cm)
    • Covered by Medicare and Medicaid
    • Manufacturer: Medline

  • Luxe Rollator

    • Lightweight rollator with 7” wheels
    • Extra-wide seat provides comfort
    • Height-adjustable arms, legs and backrest allow users to find a custom fit
    • Includes a nylon carry-all bag and a cup holder
    • Partially covered by Medicare and Medicaid
    • Manufacturer: MedlineITAL CARE

  • 3 Wheel Rollator Deluxe

    • Comes standard with basket, tray and pouch
    • Comes with frame folded and compact
    • 7.5 inch casters for indoor or outdoor use
    • Easy, one hand folding
    • Manufacturer: Drive

  • Duet Rollator

    • Combines the features of a rollator and transport chair in one unit
    • An individual can ambulate independently or be pushed safely by a caregiver
    • To use as a transport chair, the Duet has locking flip-up armrests and a flip-down footrest to aid the user
    • Comes with padded seat with carry pouch for added privacy and security of personal items
    • Manufacturer: Drive

  • Transport Chair

    • Basic Aluminum Transport Chair with 8” Wheels
    • Powder-coated aluminum frame is lightweight and durable, and the back folds down for easy storage and transport
    • Features include a seat belt for safety, comfortable nylon upholstery, and padded arms 300-lb. weight capacity
    • Covered by Medicare and Medicaid
    • Manufacturer: Medline

  • Single Point Cane Offset

    • Support users up to 300 lbs.
    • Easy-to-use, single push button adjusts height from 30 to 39 inches
    • Locking ring tightens and prevents rattling to add security and reduce irritating noise
    • Ergonomically-designed offset handle with soft, foam or rubber grip and attached wrist strap to reduce hand pressure allowing for increased stability, comfort, and convenience
    • Lightweight aluminum construction ideal for users with limited upper body strength
    • Covered by Medicare and Medicaid
    • Assorted colors

  • Folding Cane

    • Folds into four convenient parts and includes plastic carry case for easy travel and storage
    • Supports users up to 300 lbs.
    • Easy-to-use, single push button adjusts height in 1-inch increments from 33 to 37 inches
    • T-shaped handle for secure grip and better distribute weight over the cane
    • Covered by Medicare and Medicaid

  • Quad Cane (small & large base)

    • Quad-cane style for more stability compared to standard canes
    • Stand-alone capability for convenience when not in use, easily balances without requiring surface to lean on, and does not require user to bend to pick up from the floor
    • Manufactured with a 7/8-inch aluminum shaft and a steel base to perfectly balance safety with durability
    • Easy-to-use, single push button design with locking bolt quickly and securely adjusts height for safe fitting from 30 to 39 inches in 1-inch increments
    • Covered by Medicare and Medicaid

  • HurryCane

    • 8 Convenient height adjustments
    • 360° Pivoting head
    • Freestanding design
    • Anodized aluminum shaft
    • Easily folds down for storage
    • Wrist strap and travel bag included
    • Assorted colors

  • Underarm Aluminum Crutches

    • Lighter than wood, the standard aluminum crutch provides stability and durability
    • Double-extruded center tube provides additional strength to weight-bearing area
    • Pushpin adjustment makes it easy-to-adjust crutch height in 1” increments
    • Non-skid, jumbo-size vinyl contoured tips provide excellent traction
    • Covered by Medicare and Medicaid

  • Forearm Crutches

    • Vinyl coated, ergonomically contoured arm cuffs molded
    • 300 lbs. Weight Capacity
    • Push Button Adjustment
    • Covered by Medicare and Medicaid
